'''浮丝藻属'''（{{lang|la|'''''Planktothrix'''''}}），又名'''浮游藍絲藻屬'''，是一種丝状[[蓝藻|蓝藻]]<ref name=jlakes>{{cite journal |url=http://www.jlakes.org/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20080405&year_id=2008&quarter_id=4&falg=1 |author1=[[林燊|林燊]] |author2=[[彭欣|彭欣]] |author3=[[吴忠兴|吴忠兴]] |author4=[[李仁辉|李仁辉]] |year=2008 |title=我国水华蓝藻的新类群——阿氏浮丝藻(''Planktothrix agardhii'')生理特性 |journal=[[湖泊科学_(期刊)|湖泊科学]] (Journal of Lake Science) |volume=20 |issue=4 |pages=437-442 |accessdate=2016-07-20 |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2016-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825194207/http://www.jlakes.org/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20080405&year_id=2008&quarter_id=4&falg=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本屬的[[模式種|模式種]]是[[阿氏浮丝藻|阿氏浮丝藻]]（''Planktothrix agardhii''）<ref name=jlakes /><ref name="komarek">{{cite journal |last1=Komárek |first1=J |last2=Komárková |first2=J |year=2004 |title=Taxonomic review of the cyanoprokaryotic genera ''Planktothrix'' and ''Planktothricoides'' |journal=Czech Phycology |volume=4 |pages=1–18 |url=http://fottea.czechphycology.cz/_contents/CP4-2004-01.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |language=en |access-date=2016-07-19 |archive-date=2009-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090711031539/http://fottea.czechphycology.cz/_contents/CP4-2004-01.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。與其他[[顫藻目|顫藻目]]的物種一樣，浮丝藻属的物種沒有{{link-en|異型細胞|Heterocyst}}與{{link-en|厚壁孢子|Akinete}}<ref name=jlakes /><ref name=ntm>{{cite web |url=http://formosa.ntm.gov.tw/seaweeds/b/b3_04.asp |title=形態與分類-分類-藍藻植物門 |publisher=[[國立臺灣博物館|國立臺灣博物館]] |accessdate=2016-07-20 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2020-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201211203/http://formosa.ntm.gov.tw/seaweeds/b/b3_04.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其獨特之處在於其[[浮游植物|浮游植物]]特性、[[毛状体|毛状体]]單生、具有气囊结构<ref name="komarek1">{{cite journal |last1=Komarek |first1=J |year=2003 |title=Planktic oscillatorialean cyanoprokaryotes (short review according to combined phenotype and molecular aspects) |journal=[[Hydrobiologia|Hydrobiologia]] |volume=502 |pages=367–382 |language=en }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Anagnostidis |first1=K |last2=Komárek |first2=J. |title=Modern approach to the classification system of cyanophytes 3-Oscillatoriales |journal=Algological Studies/Archiv für Hydrobiologie |year=1988 |volume=50—53 |pages=327—472 |language=en }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://ir.ihb.ac.cn/bitstream/342005/17587/3/%25E6%25B4%25B1%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25B5%25AE%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E8%2593%259D%25E8%2597%25BB%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%25B0%258F%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E4%25B8%259D%25E8%2597%25BB%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25B1%25BB%25E5%25AD%25A6%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25AE%25A8%25E8%25AE%25BA.pdf.txt |author1=[[卫志宏|卫志宏]] |author2=[[朱梦灵|朱梦灵]] |author3=[[虞功亮|虞功亮]] |author4=[[李仁辉|李仁辉]] |title=洱海的浮游蓝藻布氏常丝藻及其分类学的讨论 |journal=[[水生生物学报|水生生物学报]] |volume=36 |issue=6 |date=2012-09-11 |accessdate=2016-07-21 |language=zh-hans |doi=10.3724/SP.J.1035.2012.01171 }}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。在須田彰一郎等人發表成果之前<ref name=Suda-etal-2002>{{cite journal |title=Taxonomic revision of water-bloom-forming species of oscillatorioid cyanobacteria |first1=Shoichiro |last1=Suda |first2=Makoto M. |last2=Watanabe |first3=Shigeto |last3=Otsuka |first4=Aparat |last4=Mahakahant |first5=Wichien |last5=Yongmanitchai |first6=Napavarn |last6=Nopartnaraporn |first7=Yongding |last7=Liu |first8=John G. |last8=Day |journal=International Journal of Systematic and Evolutionary Microbiology |year=2002 |volume=52 |pages=1577–1595 |language=en  |doi=10.1099/ijs.0.01834-0}}</ref>，本屬部分物種被歸入[[顫藻屬|顫藻屬]]。

{{link-en|安東尼·瓦爾斯比|A.E. Walsby}}就本屬物種的生態及生理學發表過大量文獻，當中更把物種產生微囊藻素的[[合成酶|合成酶]]的相關基因序列出來<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Christiansen |first1=G |last2=Fastner |first2=J |last3=Erhard |first3=M |last4=Börner |first4=T |last5=Dittmann |first5=E |year=2003 |title=Microcystin biosynthesis in Planktothrix: genes, evolution, and manipulation
|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_2003-01_185_2/page/564 |journal=J Bacteriol |volume=185 |pages=564–572 |language=en |doi=10.1128/JB.185.2.564-572.2003}}</ref>。

造成綠色[[水華|水華]]的阿氏浮丝藻與形成[[紅潮|紅潮]]的[[红色浮丝藻|红色浮丝藻]]在北半球的湖泊很常見<ref name=who1>{{cite book |last1=Sivonen |first1=K. |last2=Jones |first2=G. |year=1999 |chapter=Cyanobacterial toxins |pages=41–111 |editor=I. Chorus and J. Bertram |title=Toxic cyanobacteria in water: a guide to public health significance, monitoring and management |publisher=E&FN Spon |location=London |url=http://www.who.int/water_sanitation_health/resourcesquality/toxcyanobacteria.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |language=en |access-date=2016-07-19 |archive-date=2021-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221001915/https://www.who.int/water_sanitation_health/resourcesquality/toxcyanobacteria.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，會產生強烈的{{link-en|肝毒素|Hepatotoxicity}}，稱為{{link-en|微囊藻毒素|Microcystin}}。微囊藻毒素為[[水質|飲用水汙染]]的來源之一，對肝有害<ref name=who1 /><ref name=who2>{{cite web |title=Cyanobacterial Toxins: Microcystin-LR in drinking water ''Background document for development of WHO Guidelines for Drinking Water Quality'' |url=http://www.who.int/water_sanitation_health/dwq/chemicals/cyanobactoxins.pdf |publisher=[[世界衛生組織|WHO]] |accessdate=2011-06-24 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111163546/https://www.who.int/water_sanitation_health/dwq/chemicals/cyanobactoxins.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而且對熱的抗性高，甚至以[[活性碳|活性碳]]吸附、加入[[氯|氯]]或[[臭氧|臭氧]]消毒也無法完全消除<ref name="udn">{{cite web|url=http://mag.udn.com/mag/campus/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=406821 |author=[[鄚朝陽|鄚朝陽]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120819040538/http://mag.udn.com/mag/campus/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=406821 |title=水庫水質解析／恐怖微囊藻毒 喝了恐罹肝炎 |publisher=聯合報 |date=2012-08-13 |accessdate=2016-07-21 |archivedate=2012-08-19 |language=zh-hant |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

